                "url": "/topics/could"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/david_crane_227870",
        "quote": "One week before Pitfall! was to be released, I only gave you one life to play the whole game. I was experimenting with that concept as sort of the ultimate challenge.",
